      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an affordable price, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer who values function and value over cosmetics. It starts, runs, and offers a solid opportunity for commuting, errands, or as a backup vehicle. Priced to reflect its age and overall condition, it presents a straightforward purchase from a seller focused on transparency. A smart option for anyone seeking inexpensive mobility without unnecessary hype.",
