    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a handy spare, or a fun little project to tinker with. It\u2019s priced fairly for what it is and sold with a straightforward, no-nonsense approach. If you want something inexpensive and usable without spending a fortune, this could be a great fit.",
