    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong candidate for someone wanting an affordable driver or solid project with good bones. This car shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but it presents as a complete, mechanically straightforward platform with plenty of life left for the right owner. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, steering feels connected, and it offers the kind of analog, no-nonsense driving character enthusiasts appreciate. A practical entry point for a commuter, weekend tinkering build, or parts-saving restoration. Priced to move and well worth a look if you want value over polish.",
      "price": 5950.0,
