      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough for someone who sees potential where others see a blank canvas. This car has the kind of lived-in character that gives it personality, and with the right owner, it could be a rewarding daily runabout, weekend tinkering project, or budget-friendly set of wheels. It offers an inviting opportunity to get into ownership at an approachable price, with plenty of room to make it your own and enjoy the journey along the way.",
